{
  "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "这幅无穷复杂的图案，来自一个短得不能再短的公式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "取一个复数 z，把它平方，再加上一个常数 c，如此反复。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "就这么一句迭代规则，却生长出数学中最著名的分形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "escape",
      "line_id": "escape-1",
      "filename": "escape-escape-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/escape-escape-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.63,
      "size": 42048,
      "text": "从零开始迭代，如果这个数列的模始终有界，我们就说 c 属于曼德博集。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "escape",
      "line_id": "escape-2",
      "filename": "escape-escape-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/escape-escape-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "如果模冲破了二，它就会一路奔向无穷，我们记下它逃逸所用的步数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "escape",
      "line_id": "escape-3",
      "filename": "escape-escape-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/escape-escape-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "把逃逸步数映射成颜色，边界附近便燃起层层叠叠的火焰。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "julia",
      "line_id": "julia-1",
      "filename": "julia-julia-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/julia-julia-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "现在反过来，把常数 c 固定住，让初始的 z 扫过整个平面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "julia",
      "line_id": "julia-2",
      "filename": "julia-julia-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/julia-julia-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "不逃逸的那些初值组成的图案，就是这个 c 对应的朱利亚集。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "julia",
      "line_id": "julia-3",
      "filename": "julia-julia-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/julia-julia-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "每选一个 c，就得到一幅独一无二的朱利亚集。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "duality",
      "line_id": "duality-1",
      "filename": "duality-duality-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/duality-duality-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "曼德博集其实是朱利亚集的一张地图。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "duality",
      "line_id": "duality-2",
      "filename": "duality-duality-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/duality-duality-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.95,
      "size": 47232,
      "text": "当 c 落在曼德博集内部，朱利亚集是连成一片的；落在外部，它就碎成尘埃。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "duality",
      "line_id": "duality-3",
      "filename": "duality-duality-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/duality-duality-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "所以曼德博集的每一个点，都在诉说另一个世界的连通与否。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "切换不同的参数 c，看朱利亚集在树枝、螺旋与尘埃之间变形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "不断放大边界，你会发现无穷小处仍藏着完整的自己。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "一条平方迭代，逃逸时间染色，画出了曼德博与朱利亚集。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "曼德博集索引着所有朱利亚集的连通性，简单孕育无穷。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mandelbrot-julia",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mandelbrot-julia/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "这就是复动力系统的分形之美，我们下次再见。"
    }
  ],
